  "description": "High nonlinearity gives this bowed string its coarse, rosin-on-catgut texture. Excitation near the bridge with narrow width creates the scratchy sul ponticello character. Physics envelope has a fast attack and low sustain — the bite hits hard then the harmonic richness settles. Random init shape.",
